listitem.para:
The &rpi;'s main power source is the Micro USB connector. If your &rpi;
comes with a power supply, it is recommended to use the bundled power
supply only.

sect3.para:
Raspbian is the de-facto default distribution for the &rpi;. The following
paragraphs provide a short overview of differences between &productname;
for ARM on the &rpi; and Raspbian.
